# PAYLAŞTIKÇA | Bilgi Paylaştıkça Çoğalır!

This is a responsive and modern multi-section website built with **HTML**, **CSS**, **JavaScript**, and **Bootstrap**. The site is designed in Turkish and focuses on content sharing and user engagement.

## 🎯 Project Overview

**PAYLAŞTIKÇA** is a sample informational website that features:
- A responsive navigation bar
- An interactive image carousel
- Clean sectioned layout for pages like Hakkımızda (About), Ekibimiz (Our Team), Galeri (Gallery), and İletişim (Contact)


#Screen Recording







## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Fully responsive layout using Bootstrap 5
- ✅ Smooth navigation with anchor links
- ✅ Image carousel for showcasing visuals
- ✅ Well-structured HTML/CSS
- ✅ Turkish content, easy to localize

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (vanilla)
- Bootstrap 5




